title: Christian Death Live 1993 Video SVCD
description:
Christian Death Live 1993, reunion show with the original band, featuring Rozz Williams.

Christian Death Live 1993 SVCD, with 320k MP3 sound.  This is not a copy of the later bad DVD version, which was mickey mouse vhs transfer with bad 192k mp3 sound.  This is one I transfered from my old VHS video, which aside from a couple of early crinks, looks and sounds better than the DVD version of the show.

This again is a SVCD, which you can watch the mpeg file in any media player or burn it onto a CD rom as a SVCD(with Nero for example), which plays on most dvd players.
